<p>Dave Hamilton and John F. Braun are back, and this show&rsquo;s totally action-packed. Great tips, awesome listener questions, and good stuff. Always remember you can listen to the live stream while the show is being recorded (follow <a href="http://twitter.com/macgeekgab" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">@MacGeekGab </a>on twitter or <a href="http://facebook.com/MacGeekGab" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Facebook</a> to find out when it&rsquo;s happening). Download today&hellip; and enjoy!</p>
